    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/50888b1eee270783f8a231dc0c6ef076.poster.avif?t=1754055205\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/50888b1eee270783f8a231dc0c6ef076.webm?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/50888b1eee270783f8a231dc0c6ef076.mp4?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《Riot Operator》是一款即时动态的暴动危机处理游戏。在惊险的模拟场景中，你将检验自己对警队和医疗单位的管理技能。在世界各地的真实地点维持和平。市民的安全掌握在你手中。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/f98224712e7213bca0b5ac25f6a0e509.poster.avif?t=1754055205\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/f98224712e7213bca0b5ac25f6a0e509.webm?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/f98224712e7213bca0b5ac25f6a0e509.mp4?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择正确的策略</h2><br>不同的情况需要不同的解决方案。将每个单位派到合适的地点，并在地图上确定各个事件的优先级。根据情况选择不同的队型，管理资源并维护你的声誉。抓捕激进的暴徒，保护市民安全，确保你的行动成功。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/1455b389fe1a20144f9c0798d0eb7259.poster.avif?t=1754055205\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/1455b389fe1a20144f9c0798d0eb7259.webm?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/1455b389fe1a20144f9c0798d0eb7259.mp4?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级你的队伍</h2><br>自定义和升级你的队伍及装备来对抗激进的暴徒。做好应对纵火、石块、路障以及双方重伤的准备。升级你的队员，为他们提供盾牌、手铐和医疗包等多种装备，确保你的行动成功。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/271f8291f2e65669645fc109dc7a1725.poster.avif?t=1754055205\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/271f8291f2e65669645fc109dc7a1725.webm?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454490/extras/271f8291f2e65669645fc109dc7a1725.mp4?t=1754055205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >处理真实暴乱事件</h2><br>暴乱以近年来的真实事件为原型。你需要尽快消除潜在威胁，证明自己有能力应对它们。千万不要失败！一旦局势失控，暴徒将破坏他们行进路线上的一切！",
